data.description: Best value, great new price! Enjoy sunset views and fireworks from your rear porch in this immaculate Sienna Model Corner Townhouse in this sidewalk community at Hamlin Reserve. Crafted and constructed as a showcase unit, this home boasts many premium upgrades.  This end unit offers a bright and open floorplan with premium plank flooring, spacious eat in kitchen with large island, SS appliances, shaker cabinets and pantry.  Primary suite on the main level with patio access and en-suite with walk-in shower and double vanities. The upper level hosts three generously sized bedrooms, one with an en-suite bath, a laundry room as well as a versatile loft.  The screened porch leads out to a paver patio and low maintenance turf that is perfect for entertaining. Oversized rear access 2 car garage. Located across the street from the clubhouse enjoy easy access to all this community has to offer including a resort-style pool, clubhouse, a playground and a dedicated dog park. Amazing location with easy and convenient access to major highways, premier shopping and dining, golf and all the area's major attractions. Don't miss this amazing opportunity! Check out the 3D tour online!
